  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "1. Install required software packages with python pip"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Use a high python version( 3.8 or above ) to install these packages:"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "pip install sphinx     （Version: 7.3.7）",
        "pip install pillow        （Version: 10.3.0）",
        "pip install sphinxcontrib-plantuml   （Version: 0.30）",
        "pip install sphinx-rtd-theme               （Version: 2.0.0）",
        "pip install sphinx_needs  （Version: 2.1.0）",
        "pip install breathe             （Version: 4.35.0）",
        "pip install doxysphinx         （Version: 3.3.8）"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "PS: if not use a high python version, doxysphinx will not be installed successfully ,the error is like below:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Note: please put the python path in your system environment variables path"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-6-4_18-44-1.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-6-4_18-44-1.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-6-21_17-1-40.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-6-21_17-1-40.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "python version:"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-12-20_13-13-18.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-12-20_13-13-18.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "sphinx-build --version as below:"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-12-20_13-11-14.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-12-20_13-11-14.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "2. Download chery 8255 code"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "After downloading the code, you will see a swcdd folder in below path:"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-6-4_19-7-50.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-6-4_19-7-50.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "3. Modify need.py file"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Find you need.py file, you can search in cmd with command <pip show sphinx-needs>"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-7-31_11-8-5.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-7-31_11-8-5.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "modify file context:"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-7-31_11-10-16.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-7-31_11-10-16.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "comment line 768 and add cal_hashed_id = str(uuid.uuid4()).replace('-','').upper()"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-7-31_11-11-26.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-7-31_11-11-26.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "4. Modify conf.py Doxyfile  and swrs_index.rst"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "add one line \"needs_id_length = 8  # Length of the ID suffix\" as below in conf.py file"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-8-7_11-31-22.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-8-7_11-31-22.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "doxyfile changed :"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-8-7_11-33-59.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-8-7_11-33-59.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Add unittest folder :"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-8-8_16-44-30.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-8-8_16-44-30.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Exclude .h file to avoid duplication ID error:"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-8-8_16-45-50.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-8-8_16-45-50.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "swrs_index.rst changed:"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-8-7_11-37-0.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-8-7_11-37-0.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Patch you can follow:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "[cheryD01] add SM14 startup, sm18 clk mon uds (811354) · Gerrit Code Review (bosch.com)"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "5. Create a build folder in SM's sphinx subfolder and execute commands"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Use ADC_Controller module as example："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "1）Run cmd in build path"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "2) Execute Cmake configuration command as picture below:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "\"xxx\\bin\\cmake.exe\" -DCMAKE_MAKE_PROGRAM=xxx\\bin\\mingw32-make.exe .. -G \"MinGW Makefiles\""
    },
    {
      "type": "code_block",
      "language": "",
      "content": "PS C:\\KANG\\01_Projects\\chery8255\\Config\\FuSa\\swcdd\\ADC_Controller\\sphinx\\build> C:\\VP_ArtifactoryTools\\cmake\\3.14.2\\bin\\cmake.exe -DCMAKE_MAKE_PROGRAM=C:\\toolbase\\mingw\\4.8.1\\bin\\mingw32-make.exe .. -G \"MinGW Makefiles\"\n-- Now is windows\n-- Configuring done\n-- Generating done\n-- Build files have been written to: C:/KANG/01_Projects/chery8255/Config/FuSa/swcdd/ADC_Controller/sphinx/build"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Replace your cmake.exe file path and mingw32-make.exe file path with below path"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-6-4_19-26-4.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-6-4_19-26-4.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "After running successfully, you can see some files generated in build folder"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-6-4_19-29-25.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-6-4_19-29-25.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "3)Run cmake --build . -- VERBOSE=1 in cmd window"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "After running, you will see a new _build folder in the path, and swcdd is generated within it."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-6-5_9-54-17.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-6-5_9-54-17.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Sphinx%20generate%20SWRS/SWCDD/UDS%20in%20Windows%20Environment/image-2024-6-5_9-54-39.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Sphinx generate SWRS_SWCDD_UDS in Windows Environment/image-2024-6-5_9-54-39.png"
    }
